Introduction

Yeonje, formerly known as Hyeseong and born as Yang Hye-sun, is a South Korean singer under NMS. She is a member of the girl group ALICE.

She appeared and competed in the show MIXNINE. On April 11, 2022, ELRIS was rebranded to ALICE, and Hyeseong changed her stage name to Yeonje.

On May 3, 2024, she announced her departure from the group in a letter to fans on Instagram. On May 29, 2024, NMS announced that Yeonje had renewed her exclusive contract with them to be represented in acting and musical theater.
